\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 22. G. polyanthos} R. de Roemer ex Willk.,{\i   Linnaea }{\b 25}: 20 (1852). Like {\b 21}(a) but up to 200 cm; pulvini with spinose stipules; standard always uniformly, densely sericeous. •{\i   S.W. Spain, S. & E.C. Portugal}. Hs Lu.
